setConfig.description: The message allows to set platform parameters

pauseProgram.description: The message allows to pause the program

resumeProgram.description: The message allows to exit from pause mode returning to the cycle previously in execution

stopProgram.description: The message allows to stop the program

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_SMART.description: Thanks to Artificial Intelligence, this program automatically adapts the washing parameters and times. At the end you can consult a report with the savings and the results obtained. Recommended for cotton, synthetic and blends, normally soiled.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_QUICK_15.description: A complete super-rapid cycle (wash, rinse, and spin), suitable for slightly dirty cottons and mixed fabrics.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_SPIN.description: Drain and (adjustable) spin cycle. The spin can be removed if you want to drain only.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_COTTONS.description: Cycle designed to develop the maximum degree of washing for cotton garments, even when fully loaded. Final spin at maximum speed (adjustable).

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_SYNTHETIC_AND_COLOURE.description: Wash cycle designed for synthetic or mixed fabrics, with a gentle final spin that reduces the formation of wrinkles.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_HANDWASH_WOOL.description: This program allows a delicate washing cycle, particularly suited to garments specified as "Machine-Washable" Wool fabrics. The "pulse" action of the drum ensures treatment equal only to hand washing.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_20_DEGREES.description: This innovative program allows you to wash different fabrics and colors together, such as cottons, synthetics and mixed fabrics at only 20°C and provides excellent cleaning. Consumption on this program is about 40% of a conventional 40°C cotton wash.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_ECO_40_60_DEGREES.description: The ECO 40-60 program is able to clean normally soiled cotton laundry declared to be washable at 40°C or 60°C, together in the same cycle. This program is used to assess the compliance with EU Ecodesign legislation (environmentally friendly product design).

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_MIX.description: Wash cycle designed for synthetic or mixed fabrics, with a gentle final spin that reduces the formation of wrinkles.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_ALLERGY.description: This program offers the possibility of obtaining a deep cleaning of your cotton garments, sanitizing them and eliminating any bacteria. Provide efficient washing at high temperature. Recommended for small loads.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_REFRESH.description: To refresh your clothes, even your delicate ones in a highly effective and innovative manner, using vapour technology to remove odours, fine dust and allergens while reducing creases and softening the fabrics.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_DUVET.description: It is a program for washing small duvets. The high water level guarantees complete cleaning of the padding.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_SHIRTS.description: Cycle optimised for washing everyday shirts (cotton and mixed), limiting the creation of wrinkles.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_AUTOCLEAN.description: Designed to clean the washing machine drum. Do not start the program with laundry in the machine. Use only powder detergent or a specific cleaning product. The App will suggest when it's time to launch it.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_SPORT.description: Made to remove dirt from technical clothing used for the gym and sports. The program includes a low temperature wash, recommended for small loads of synthetic items.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_BABYCARE.description: A cycle designed to take good care of baby clothes and eliminate all detergent residues

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_CHECKUP.description: Short diagnostic cycle (5-25 minutes) to check the correct functioning of the main components of the appliance. **To be started with an empty drum**. At the end you will receive a notification with the results of the Check-Up on your smartphone.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_DELICATE_CRADLE.description: This program is suitable for washing delicate fabrics. The wash cycle alternates between the gentle agitation of the drum and rest periods. The higher level of water ensures the best washing performance.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_QUICK_WASH_57.description: This rapid cycle is designed to obtain the highest quality of washing in just 57 minutes, at 40°C and with small loads.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.HQD_RINSE.description: This program performs rinses with a medium spin (which can be reduced or excluded). It is useful after hand washing or bleaching.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_COTTON.description: Cycle designed to develop the maximum degree of washing for cotton garments, even when fully loaded. Final spin at maximum speed (adjustable).

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_SYNTHETIC.description: Wash cycle designed for synthetic or mixed fabrics, with a gentle final spin that reduces the formation of wrinkles.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_MIXED.description: Wash cycle designed for synthetic or mixed fabrics, with a gentle final spin that reduces the formation of wrinkles.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_DELICATE.description: This program is suitable for washing delicate fabrics. The wash cycle alternates between the gentle agitation of the drum and rest periods. The higher level of water ensures the best washing performance.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_COLOURED.description: This program allows you to wash together laundry of different colors and fabrics. Washing and rinsing are optimised in the drum rotation rhythms and in the water levels. The gentle action centrifuge ensures reduced wrinkling on the fabrics.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_WOOL.description: This program allows a delicate washing cycle, particularly suited to garments specified as "Machine-Washable" Wool fabrics. The "pulse" action of the drum ensures treatment equal only to hand washing.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_RAPID_14.description: A complete super-rapid cycle (wash, rinse, and spin), suitable for slightly dirty cottons and mixed fabrics.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_RAPID_30.description: A complete rapid cycle (wash, rinse, and spin), suitable for slightly dirty cottons and mixed fabrics.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_RAPID_44.description: Short washing cycle recommended for a lightly soiled reduced load. Reduce the amount of detergent normally used to avoid waste.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_RAPID_59.description: This cycle is designed to obtain the highest quality of washing in less than one hour. It is able to wash up to a temperature of 60°C.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_SPORT.description: This program is specially designed to wash mixed sportswear fabrics that cannot be washed on hotter programs and is designed to remove the dirt and staining created by participation in sports activities. (1/2 of the maximum load).

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_SPIN.description: Drain and (adjustable) spin cycle. The spin can be removed if you want to drain only.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_RINSE.description: This program performs 3 rinses with a medium spin (which can be reduced or excluded). It is useful after hand washing or bleaching.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_BABY_SANITIZER.description: This cycle sanitises all resistant children's clothing at 60°C, without a trace of detergent.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_BACKPACKS.description: For quick cleaning of backpacks and pouches, this cycle removes dust and enhances colors.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_BATHROBE.description: For washing bathrobes, towels, and resistant spongy garments, ensuring the total removal of detergent.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_BED_LINEN.description: The ideal cycle for the accurate washing of your white cotton or synthetic bed linens.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_CASHMERE.description: Cashmere care program. The delicate oscillations of the drum allow a treatment equal to that of your hands.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_CUDDLY_TOYS.description: Very gentle program for the accurate washing of stuffed animals.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_CURTAINS.description: Program designed to wash white curtains. The low spin speed ensures limited wrinkling.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_DIVING_SUITS.description: Cycle specifically designed for the delicate washing of diving suits, preserving their fibres.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_DOWN_JACKETS.description: A specific program designed for quilted jackets. The high water level ensures precise washing and rinsing.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_DELICATE_TABLECL.description: For the precise washing of your most delicate tablecloths, thanks to its controlled temperature and high water level.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_DENIM_JEANS.description: The program thoroughly cleans the fibres of your jeans while respecting its colors, wash after wash.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_CHOCOLATE_STAINS.description: Program designed for the removal of chocolate stains from resistant cotton and mixed fabrics.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_WINE_STAINS.description: A cycle designed to eliminate all wine stains from resistant cotton and mixed garments.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_FRUIT_STAINS.description: A high temperature cycle designed to eliminate all fruit stains from resistant cotton and mixed clothing.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_BLOOD_STAINS.description: Cycle designed to remove blood stains from your resistant cotton and / or mixed clothes.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_PERFECT_WHITE.description: A perfect cycle to preserve the whiteness of your resistant cotton and mixed clothes, day after day.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_COLORED_ANTI_STA.description: Cycle designed to remove the most common stains, even on colored fabrics.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_BLEACHING.description: Specific cycle for the preliminary removal of stains with liquid bleach (without detergent). Once finished, proceed with traditional washing.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_ANTI_MITES.description: A program created to remove dust particles. Rinses remove any residues from cotton and/or synthetic garments.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_SPORT_ANTI_ODOR.description: Program designed to remove dirt and stains from mixed sports garments that cannot be washed at high temperatures.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_PETS.description: The perfect program designed to eliminate odours and pet hair on resistant cotton and mixed clothing.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_DELICATE_ANTIALL.description: The program allows to remove 80% of allergens from delicate fabrics, preserving their fibres.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_NEW_CLOTHES.description: Rapid program designed to remove residues and freshen up newly purchased clothes.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_LINGERIE.description: A special cycle for delicate lingerie, with gentle pulsing movements of the drum to simulate hand washing.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_MATS.description: Program designed for washing bath mats, removing dirt from the fibres and preserving colors.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_TRAINERS.description: Rapid program designed to wash sport shoes and trainers.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_MEN_S_TROUSERS.description: Program for washing trousers (cotton and mixed), without any possible damage or creases.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_SILK.description: Program for silk garments, like a hand wash, with very slow pulsing drum movements and high water level.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_SKI_SUIT.description: A special cycle designed to gently wash your ski suits.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_DELICATE_COLORS.description: A cycle for more delicate colored clothes, to minimise the wrinkles, thanks to its gentle final spin.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_DARK.description: A cycle designed to wash all your dark clothing (cottons and mixed), with the greatest care.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_SWIMSUITS_AND_BI.description: Short washing cycle that is perfect for rinsing swimsuits after use in the sea or pool, without any damage.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_TABLECLOTHS.description: Cycle designed to remove dirt from your more resistant white tablecloths, ensuring very limited wrinkling.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_TECHNICAL_FABRIC.description: Program studied for the treatment of technical fabrics, ensuring their perfect elasticity.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_TECHNICAL_JACKET.description: A cycle designed to wash all your technical jackets without damaging fabrics and colors.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_MASKS_SANIFICATI.description: Cycle developed for the sanitization of face masks, gloves and garments made of resistant cotton, at 60°C. To enhance the sanitizing effect, we suggest you use a specific laundry additive. The duration will automatically adapt to the load actually introduced. Check the washing label.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_MASKS_REFRESH.description: Cycle designed to wash face masks, gloves and garments made of synthetic fabrics. Use sanitizing laundry additives or, in case of white fabrics, bleach. Check the washing label. This is not a sanitization cycle.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_COLD_WASH.description: Cycle designed for cold washing your most delicate garments

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_COLORED.description: This cycle washes all your colored clothes (cotton and mixed), normally soiled, with the maximum care.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_COLORED_DELICATE.description: A cycle for the more delicate colored clothes, to minimize the creases, thanks to its gentle final spin action.

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_DELICATE_DARK.description: Ideal cycle for washing your most delicate colored garments

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_DELICATE_WHITES.description: Ideal cycle for the treatment of your most delicate whites

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_HANDWASH.description: Extra delicate cycle designed for light "hand wash only" items

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_HANDWASH_COLORED.description: Extra delicate cycle designed for "hand wash only" items

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_HANDWASH_DARK.description: Extra delicate cycle designed for dak "hand wash only" items

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_RESISTANT_COLORE.description: Program specifically created for washing resistant colored items

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_RESISTANT_DARK.description: Program specifically created for washing resistant dark items

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_RESISTANT_WHITES.description: Program specifically created for washing resistant whites

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_WHITES.description: Program specifically created for washing resistant light items

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_ARIEL_COLD_CYCLE.description: This cycle is recommended for brilliant cleaning even in cold wash to reduce carbon footprint & be more responsible to environment with Ariel PODS

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_ARIEL_FRESH_CYCL.description: This cycle is recommended for extra fabric protection and freshness by unleashing ARIEL PODS anti-fuzz, anti-stretch and color protection technologies

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_ARIEL_CLEAN_CYCL.description: This cycle is recommended for ultimate cleaning even in tough stains with the help of Ariel PODS

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_PETS_HAIR_REMOVA.description: Cycle dedicated to the removal of animal hair from clothes and home fabrics, with average levels of soiling (cushions, sofas, etc.)

PROGRAMS.WM_WD.IOT_WASH_PETS_ODOURS_STAI.description: Cycle dedicated to the removal of odours and food stains, capable of sanitising resistant or mixed fabrics, with high levels of soiling (with steam)
